    "title": "Borosil Global Group is Hiring: Floor Manager (Entry-Level)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Borosil Global Group! We are hiring a Floor Manager for our Srinagar team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Borosil Global Group:\nBorosil Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Loss Prevention\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Borosil Global Group!",
